### 1. Create Playlist
POST http://localhost:8080/api/playlist
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer USER_TOKEN

{
  "name": "My Playlist",
  "description": "Test playlist",
  "channelId": "CHANNEL_ID"
}

###

### 2. Update Playlist
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/playlist/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer USER_TOKEN

{
  "name": "Updated Playlist",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "orderNum": 1
}

###

### 3. Change Status
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/playlist/1/status?status=PUBLIC
Authorization: Bearer USER_TOKEN

###

### 4. Delete
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/playlist/1
Authorization: Bearer USER_TOKEN

###

### 5. Pagination (ADMIN)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/playlist/pagination?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN

###

### 6. By UserId (ADMIN)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/playlist/by-user/1
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN

###

### 7. My Playlists
GET http://localhost:8080/api/playlist/my
Authorization: Bearer USER_TOKEN

###

### 8. Channel Playlists
GET http://localhost:8080/api/playlist/channel/CHANNEL_ID

###

### 9. Playlist Detail
GET http://localhost:8080/api/playlist/1

###